data.description: Fresh and Ready to Buy! This two-story starter home has been freshly painted and restored! Walk in to incredibly tall ceilings and lovely laminate floors in the formal living/dining combo room. Those floors extend into the informal family room with traditional brick fireplace. A Half bathroom downstairs is perfect for visiting guests. Laundry comes with Washer and Dryer! Walk upstairs and overlook the formal living from the open loft, where you also have access to the balcony and pretty mountain views. Head outside where there's tons of space and green grass in the backyard to enjoy!
